# .dockerignore — shrink the build context, avoid leaking local artifacts.

**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.git/
**/.github/
**/.claude/
**/node_modules/
**/Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store

# Secret files — must NEVER go into the image
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/secrets.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pfx
**/*.key
**/*.pem

# Doc / IaC not needed in the runtime image
docs/
# but docs/schemas/*.json are embedded into Infrastructure.dll at build time → must keep
!docs/schemas/
!docs/schemas/**
infra/
tests/fixtures/
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
